<P><PB N="248" REF="264"><NOTE PLACE="marg"><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 paragraph"></NOTE>TO conclude, I &s;hall give the prices of the different kinds of corn during this noted year of &s;carcity, famine it cannot be called, for the evil has been very remote from that dreadful judgment, by rea&s;on of the innumerable re&s;ources <HI>Britain</HI> has within it&s;elf, both from the vegetable and animal kingdoms.</P>
