<DIV3 N="10" TYPE="section">
<HEAD>X.</HEAD>
<P><HI>BRAINT HIR,</HI> of <HI>Is-dulas,</HI> lived, as I conjecture, about the time of the &s;ons of <HI>Roderic</HI> <NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">Others &s;ay that he lived about the year 650, in the time of <HI>Cadwallon,</HI> who&s;e nephew and chancellor he was.</NOTE> <HI>the Great.</HI> His po&s;terity did not much increa&s;e, for there are not many, at pre&s;ent, known to be de&s;cended from him, yet &s;ome there are.&mdash;<HI>His arms are vert, a cro&s;s flowery or.</HI></P>
